      "role": "user",
      "content": "i was looking at old photos today... just feels like i'm looking at a stranger. the person in those pictures, the one with all the plans and the energy... that person is dead. i'm just the empty shell that's left walking around. it's exhausting pretending to be alive when you know you've been gone for years.",
